Infrastructure:
- HAProxy Load Balancer with SSL termination, firewall, and monitoring agent
- Two servers with Nginx, App Server, Codebase, MySQL (Primary + Replica), firewall, and monitoring agent
- HTTPS enabled via SSL certificate
- Monitoring agents on all servers

Purpose of Elements:
- Firewalls: Restrict unauthorized access
- HTTPS: Encrypts traffic, protects user data
- Monitoring: Tracks performance, uptime, errors
- QPS Monitoring: Parse Nginx logs with agent, visualize in dashboard

Issues:
- SSL termination at LB exposes internal traffic
- One MySQL write node is a SPOF
- All-in-one servers reduce scalability and fault isolation
